So what are we going to start with?
It took me a while to think it over,
but I think we should start with Yui.
Who?
You know, the girl who does vocals for the guerrilla live concerts in the cafe.
Do Not you remember her?
She Is always so energetic, laughing away while she bullies Hinata.
She does the bands vocals and anything else she likes doing.
I think she is already found peace.
If we just give her a gentle push,
she will be able to leave this place.
That Is what I think.
If you think so, then alright.
You agree?
Okay, then let us do that.
So, how is it going on your end?
Well, it took some time...
Hand Sonic, version 5.
This is Hand Sonic version 5.

I made it like this because you told me I Am playing the cruel Angel, so I had to make it look mean.
No good?
No, that is great.
Really unpleasant.
Unpleasant?
No no, I mean really good.
Could you also grow wings?
Wings?
What would I do with those?
It Would look cool, would not it?
I have to look cool?
No, I just thought it would make you more Angel - like.
Ill think about it.
Thanks.
So, what am I supposed to do?
Oh, right.
Let Us do this
You appear while she is in band practice,
then you tell her,
Another club is complaining about the noise.”
Then you point at Yui and say,
Your guitar is especially bad.”
Because of you, the band is dead.”
That being the case, I Am confiscating that guitar.”
Then you take her guitar and leave the scene.

Just run, and head to the inner garden.
At that point Ill pretend to bump into you, and then you let go of the guitar.
Ill take it, so just run away at that point.
This way we can create a situation where I can be alone with her.
Understood.
Alright!
Now we just wait for the start of rehearsal and go!

Stop!
Yui, do not just keep going when you mess up the rhythm!
Do not you think you should concentrate on just singing or playing?
Yeah you are right, it sounds bad right now.
No way!
Iwasawa - san sang and played at the same time!
That Is because Iwasawa was good at both.
I Am trying my best too!
You Are all too strict!
Our concerts are popular are not they?
But this is a new song.
Angel?!
Because of your guitar, the band is dead.
She discovered the bands weak point in an instant!
We cannot underestimate her!
She knows music!
No way!
I thought nobody noticed!
That being the case, I Am confiscating that guitar.
Hey, Yui!
Are you okay?
Here.
Why are you alone?
She did not chase me.
See?
Without the guitar you do not go off beat.
But does not it sound kind of weak?
We need a rhythm guitar.
Should we get another side guitar player then?
What I want to say is...
The band has the most impact with the vocals also on guitar, dammit!!
Why you...
She made Hisako - san angry!
I am going to go get my guitar back!
Crap!
Hey!
Dammit, Yui!
Here she comes!
Where did she go?
There she is!
Wait up!
Whoops, sorry!
Idiot, that is too high!
My guitar!
Its fine, not a scra
Senpai protected it from Angel for me!
Where did she go, dammit!!
Geez, what is with the dammit!”
I see you are doing whatever you want, as usual.
Whatever I want?
Not really...
You got the vocal position in the band, did not you?
You Are even playing guitar.
Oh that is nothing, its just one of the things I wanted to do.
There are other things?
Yeah, lots of them.
Lots”...
No wait, let us talk somewhere else.
- Front
So, what else is there?
Do I have to tell you?
If you do not want to talk about it, that is fine.
That Is okay, Ill tell you.
I have more things I want to do than most people.
Why do you think that is?
Because, I guess...
You could not do them when you were alive?
Yep, exactly!
When I was small, I got hit by a car from behind.
After that, I became paralyzed.
I was completely bedridden.
I could not live without assistance.
I was constantly relying on my mother.
I was always thinking it was not fair to her.
I was able to watch TV, so when I saw bands on music shows I thought it would be great if I could do that too.
I see.
That turned out well then.
Yeah!
So what else do you want to do?
Well, I watched baseball matches a lot.
Did we already play baseball at the tournament?
I did not get a hit though.
Hit?
A home run!
You will not be happy till you hit a home run?
Not at all!
Once I become better in the band, I Am thinking about putting in some real practice.
Keeping both of those up will be tough.
I guess Ill ask, what else was there?
Soccer!
Soccer?!
It was popular, right!
Well it was, but...
She has too many interests!
In what world does a person try to be a musician, baseball player, and a soccer player?
I do not suppose there are any oth
Pro wrestling!
I do not understand her!
In what world...
Wait, everything she wants to do comes from TV...
But this is going to be hard...
Granting all of those dreams for her...
Alright.
Ill fulfill those dreams for you.
Let Us start with something easy.
How about we go with pro wrestling?
Pro wrestling?
What move?
German Suplex!
There
Is no way you can pull off such a flashy move!
Do a pin or something you can actually pull off!
But I Have always wanted to do the German Suplex!
And then I will win with a sleeper hold!
Do Not say such violent things so innocently!
Okay.
Let Us try it.
Really?
Yeah.
Alright!
You Are stronger than I thought!
You can do this!
Owww!!
I guess its impossible for a girl...
No, you almost did it!
That was close!
Really?
Then can we try it again?
Y - Yeah...
Can we go somewhere with grass first?
Otherwise Ill die.
You cannot die!
No, I was not joking.
I am not going to make it.
Sorry!
Ill get it right next time!
This really is the last time.
I Am going back.
Senpai!
Are you even able to pull off a bridge?
I can!
Let Us see it.
So this was the root of the problem...
Thanks to this I nearly lost consciousness several times.
Well start with bridge training then.
What?
Boring!
Just do it!
Come on, try harder!
That Is terrible, come on!
But I
Have never done this before!
If you cannot do this, you will not be able to do the German Suplex.
Ill do my best.
I Am doing it, just about!
You are shaking all over the place, but that will do.
Here I go then!
Bring it!
Her arms are fixed firmly around my waist!
There
Is no escape from this!
It is perfect!
Perfect!
German Suplex!!
One...
two...
three!
Ding ding ding!
Match over!
I did it...
I really did it!
Yay!
Banzai!
How much more of this am I going to have to deal with?
- Passageway
How about we do soccer next?
A one on one penalty kick should be fine, right?
No, I want to do a dribble shoot against 5 people!
You know, Maradona.
Well, I know that...
Okay, fine.
Leave it to me!

He cannot dance in my world right now.
Do not let me cry!
I guess so...

Secluded mountain training.
In the mountain.
IN THE MOUNTAIN.
Secluded mountain training?
Hes gone pretty far off...
So he will not be back for a while?
Ah whatever, you will do.
Could you gather up 4 other members for me?
- Mens toilet
Keep this secret from Yuri, but I got this letter from Angel.
You cannot even stand up to a single girl.
It is absurd to think you call yourself a man.
I Am surprised you know a word like absurd”.
Were you cured of idiocy?
No, even idiots can read this.
Ill beat your girly ass till you learn some guts for the sake of sportsmanship.
Ill be waiting after school at the soccer grounds.
Angel.

Did she really write this?

I cannot deal with this stupidity.
I Am going to go tell Yurippe.
I said keep it a secret from Yuri!
Why?
If you tell Yuri, it will develop into another bloodbath.
Look, it says for the sake of sportsmanship” right?
She Is saying she wants to fight fair and square with sports.
That Is why this challenge is directed at us guys.
Telling Yuri would damage our pride as men.
I see, that is a good point.
I guess the five of us will go then.
Kiss you!
That Is the spirit!
What?
Look over there.
Someone
Is there.
Is Not that Yui?
What Is she doing?
So you have come.
Kick off!

Here I come, you bastards!
I get it!
She Is the one who wrote the letter!
She must have gotten annoyed with us always being so useless that she was driven to doing this!
Alright, let us defend the goal!
Were not losing this fight!
Us men will win!
I do not really get it but...
I get it!

I kiss you!
Hinata, take goalie!
Alright!
Outta my way, damn idiots!

Take this!

What the hell was that?

Number two!

Safe!
Who Is that supposed to be?

Get her, TK!
Otonashi!

Leave it to us!
Number three!
Alright!
Woo!
Here we

Like I care!
Here I come!
Ultimate Killer Shot!!
I cannot tell whether she wants to kill me or score a goal with this shot!
Its a miracle!
Hinata!!
It went in?
Yay!
I did it!
I scored a goal!
No way...
We lost?
To Yui, by herself...
Scrambled it trouble down.
That was bad...
Let Us keep this a secret.
Yeah...
Though, she lost the ball, did not pass the goalie and went all over the place...
Well, whatever.
Alright...
Let Us move on to the next one!
<Sign: Baseball field >
Before that, how far are you trying to hit this home run?
Beyond the fence, of course!
Seriously?
Well for now, hit it as hard as you can.
I hit it!
Just hitting the ball does not mean much...
Watch the ball carefully and hit it with the center of the bat.
You Are hitting too high on the ball.
Now you are too low.
There
Is no way you will hit it with your eyes closed!
This is weak...
Come on, try harder!
I am!
One more time!

There

Huh?

Well start again tomorrow!

Yo!
Want to try?
Serious baseball.

I guess this kind of things okay too.
Come on!
You Are not hitting them at all!
Are you okay?
Let me see your hands.
No.
Show me!
I guess this is why...
I cannot do it after all...
This is enough for this dream.
Do Not give up!
Thanks for everything.
Why are you doing this for me?
Well, because you wanted to do it.
See it through to the end!
Me getting a home run would be a joke.
And even without hitting one, I was able to use my body to this extent.
That Is more than enough.
It felt like going to a club every day.
I had fun!
I told you, right?
I was paralyzed in the past, so this was amazingly fun.
So they are all fulfilled?
Fulfilled?
What is?
Everything you wanted to do when you could not move.
Oh...
There Is one more.
What?
Marriage.
The ultimate happiness for a girl.
But I cannot do housework or cleaning or anything...
Actually, I cannot do anything by myself.
I Am nothing but trouble, dragging everyone else down.
I guess no one would want to take me...
God is pretty mean...
My happiness...
It was all taken from me.
That Is not true.
Then, senpai...
will you marry me?
Ill do it!
Hinata...
Ill marry you.
I Am serious.
But...
You do not know the real me...
No matter what happens to you in the real world,
Ill marry you!
No matter what kind of sickness you have!
I cannot walk or even stand...
I said no matter what kind!!
Even if you cannot walk or stand,
or even if you cannot have kids!
Ill still marry you!
Ill always stay by your side.
The Yui I met here is not fake.
Its the real Yui!
No matter where or how I meet you, Ill fall in love with you.
If I can meet you again, against the 6 billion to 1 odds,
and even if your body cannot move,
Ill marry you.
We will not meet...
I Am always in bed at home.
I play baseball you know.
One day, Ill smash a baseball through your window,
and when I go to get it, Ill find you.
That Is how well meet.
Well end up talking, we will get along, and before I know it Ill be visiting you every day.
What do you think?
Yeah...
Hey, when that happens...
My moms always working hard by herself to take care of me...
Could you help her out?
Leave it to me.
Thank goodness...
Are you okay with that?
Of course.
What are you going to do now?
Ill help you out till the end.
There are still lots of our friends who need help.
I see.
What the hell did I just cut?
A shadow?
Explain it a bit more clearly.
That Is the only explanation I have.
Noda - san just ran here and defeated it.
Oyama - san by himself was in danger.
Danger?
What?
